Today is World Mental Health Day and we support kids' mental health and organizations like @YourMomCares and RxWell that are doing innovative, groundbreaking work in transforming how young people receive the mental health support they need.
We are donating to help continue the further development of behavioral health care that was not previously available for adolescents. Text maroon5 to 44-321 to help support this cause as well.
